---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="AI Search Visibility for Financial Advisors UK | Rank4AI" description="Get your financial advice firm recommended by ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini and Perplexity. AI search visibility for UK IFAs.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Who We Help', href: '/who-we-help/' },
      { label: 'Financial Advisors' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">By Profession</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">AI Search Visibility for Financial Advisors</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">When someone asks an AI platform "recommend an independent financial advisor near me," the platform checks multiple sources before naming anyone. FCA registration, client reviews, professional listings, and consistent descriptions all factor into whether your firm gets recommended.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Financial advice is a high-trust category. AI platforms are cautious about recommending financial services – they need strong verification signals before they will name a specific firm. This means institutional trust signals (FCA, Companies House, ICO) carry even more weight than in other sectors.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Key Signals for Financial Advisors</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">FCA registration</span> – the most important trust signal. Must be visible in structured data and consistent with the FCA register.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Specialisation clarity</span> – pensions, investments, mortgages, tax planning. AI recommends specialists more confidently than generalists.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">VouchedFor / Unbiased</span> – industry-specific directories that AI platforms reference for financial advisor recommendations.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16">
    <h2 class="!text-2xl mb-4">Find out if AI recommends your firm</h2>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
